Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.31,0:28:01.66,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\fsp0}This is a fate that brought us here watch my long shot
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.69,0:28:12.36,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\fsp0}Feel like I am falling into the flame of lies
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.36,0:28:15.00,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\fsp0}Tell me what do you want from me
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.81,0:28:19.31,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\fsp0}Trying not to step back to where I used to belong
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.31,0:28:22.04,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\fsp0}Looking for the escape from pain
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.04,0:28:26.57,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\fsp0}I will cross my fingers hoping not to be sacrificed
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.57,0:28:30.07,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}約束したんだ君とその希望に
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.07,0:28:33.90,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\fsp0}Get in the raid Get ready for the time to come
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.90,0:28:37.33,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}浮かび上がるシルエット追いかけ
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.33,0:28:40.73,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\fsp0}Drop down the reason why I'm standing here alone
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.73,0:28:44.31,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\fsp0}May be it's already too late to regain
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.53,0:28:49.71,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}運命としてかかげた灯を失くさないで
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.71,0:28:50.82,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\fsp0}Ever again
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.93,0:28:54.58,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\fsp0}What if I could right my wrongs and save you from the pain
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.58,0:29:03.97,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\fsp0\fs38}It's not enough It's not enough for me to break the rule upon this world
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.12,0:29:08.97,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\fsp0}I will never gonna leave you never wanna lose you
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.97,0:29:11.38,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\fsp0}we'll make it in the end
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.62,0:29:17.74,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\fsp0}Not backing down for real I won't trace someone else's life
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.19,0:29:19.90,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\fsp0}I know who I am
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.31,0:28:01.66,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}命运带我们走到了这里 见识我的豪赌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.69,0:28:12.36,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}仿佛落入了谎言的烈火之中
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.36,0:28:15.00,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}请告诉我 你想让我怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.81,0:28:19.31,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}为了保护我所在的家园
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.31,0:28:22.04,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}我寻找着逃脱苦难的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.04,0:28:26.57,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}我握拳祈祷不会有人牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.57,0:28:30.07,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}我保证过不会放弃你和希望
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.07,0:28:33.90,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}做好准备 直面必将到来的侵袭
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.90,0:28:37.33,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}追赶着脑海里浮现的倩影
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.33,0:28:40.73,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}舍弃掉孤独战斗的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.73,0:28:44.31,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}想夺回一切也许为时已晚
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.53,0:28:49.71,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}但也不要丢失命运给你的灯火
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.71,0:28:50.82,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}再也不要
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.93,0:28:54.58,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}如果我能改掉错误 救你于水火之中
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.58,0:29:03.97,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}那也不够我去打破这个世界的规则
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.12,0:29:08.97,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}我不会再丢下你 不会再失去你
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.97,0:29:11.38,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}我们一定能成功
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.62,0:29:17.74,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}我决不后退 决不成为别人理想的模样
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.19,0:29:19.90,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}我知道我该过怎样的人生
